<div class="p-4 p-md-5 pt-2 rounded text-body-emphasis bg-body-secondary">
  <h2> <span class="introSpan">Daily Planet:</span> A Leading Source of Information in the Digital Age</h2>
  <p>The Daily Planet is a renowned and long-standing newspaper based in India, now embracing the digital revolution with its online article and blog platform. With decades of journalistic integrity and a strong legacy of hard-hitting news reporting, the Daily Planet continues to stay relevant in today’s fast-paced, online world. It serves millions of readers with timely articles, engaging blogs, and in-depth reporting across various topics.</p>  
</div>

<div class="row">
